A former kingpin of the streets, Miles Cain Skinner (Ving Rhames) is doing life in prison.
He is feared and respected among the inmates. When Cain learns that his sentence will be
shortened only by brain cancer, his urgency to change his ways goes into overdrive. His
only desire is to save his two feuding sons, also inmates, from each other. Warden Dean
(Robert Patrick) is the only man that can help Cain with the redemption he seeks, but it
comes at a price.
